# RePIT-Framework

This framework aims at automating the process for ML-CFD cross computation. It is the extension of RePIT algorithm introduced by [J. Jeon et. al](https://arxiv.org/abs/2206.06817).

# Use the framework in development mode: 
`cd` to the root directory of the project folder, then 
`pip install -e .`
